208
00:11:33,818 --> 00:11:36,946
{\an8}<i>So the handicap system</i>
<i>in the U.S. Open is</i>

209
00:11:37,029 --> 00:11:41,117
<i>each player has a handicap from</i>
<i>between minus one when you're a beginner</i>

210
