somewhere between three and eight goals.

214
00:11:53,337 --> 00:11:57,967
{\an8}There is less than eight ten-goal players
right now in the entire world.

215
00:11:58,050 --> 00:12:02,012
<i>We have some amazing</i>
<i>ten-goal players in the U.S. Open.</i>

216
00:12:02,638 --> 00:12:05,850
<i>Most notably is,</i>
<i>of course, Adolfo Cambiaso</i>

217
00:12:06,726 --> 00:12:08,686
<i>and his son, Poroto Cambiaso.</i>

218
00:12:09,854 --> 00:12:13,107
My handicap,
I mean, right now is, is one.

219
00:12:13,899 --> 00:12:16,318
The goal is to get my handicap
to go up as much as possible.

220
00:12:16,402 --> 00:12:17,737
We haven't missed,

221
00:12:18,821 --> 00:12:20,531
{\an8}uh… a workout this whole season.

