00:12:20,614 --> 00:12:21,449
{\an8}No.

223
00:12:23,492 --> 00:12:26,370
It's such a hard sport to tackle,

224
00:12:26,454 --> 00:12:30,791
especially at, you know,
I was 40 when I first picked it up.

225
00:12:32,042 --> 00:12:36,213
I have to work extra hard
to do what's best for the team.

226
00:12:37,089 --> 00:12:40,718
And it's, you know, it's my team,
so I don't want to let the boys down.

227
00:12:40,801 --> 00:12:43,262
What the fuck am I doing here?

228
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:47,349
{\an8}Foul, it's how it is.

229
00:12:47,433 --> 00:12:48,392
{\an8}Foul.

230
00:12:48,476 --> 00:12:51,479
{\an8}Robi and I started La Fe together
three years ago.

231
00:12:52,188 --> 00:12:54,648
What separates La Fe
from every other team?

232
